# --- GitHub Actions ---
# Configure os mesmos valores em: Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions
# O workflow .github/workflows/deploy.yml usa os secrets no lugar deste arquivo.
# Obrigatórios: VPS_SSH_PASS (ou VPS_SSH_KEY), MAILCOW_PASS, MAILCOW_API_KEY,
#               CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN, CLOUDFLARE_ZONE_ID
